  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You live alone. Someone is coming over. You must mop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a raccoon who has to mop up the floor in anticipation of big changes. Using a mouse or a controller, you need to carefully mop between and around corners to avoid soaking your furniture. As you get further into the game, you'll grow your family and accrue more and more furniture, making it increasingly difficult. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Must Mop is a short arcade style experience about fine motor dexterity and precision, with a lighthearted story to follow.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You live alone. Someone is coming over. You must mop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a raccoon who has to mop up the floor in anticipation of big changes. Using a mouse or a controller, you need to carefully mop between and around corners to avoid soaking your furniture. As you get further into the game, you'll grow your family and accrue more and more furniture, making it increasingly difficult. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Must Mop is a short arcade style experience about fine motor dexterity and precision, with a lighthearted story to follow.</p>",
